comments.body:
@runapp I was wondering if you found documented anywhere that you need to add your own UID/GID to the configuration files.  Possibly newer versions behave the same way, I I think it is just a wrong configuration.

Since it seems to work with a regular configuration and that is related to newuidmap/newgidmap that are not under Podman control, I am going to close this issue.

Please feel free to add more comments or reopen it if you still think it is Podman doing something wrong.
